{"tid":2318141,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"外國研究指手遊玩家智商最低","createTime":"2020-12-09T06:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T06:31:04.000Z","uid":362414,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"402fcde736134d5de07e5e6f202a1c91be12e4a5","tid":2318141,"uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"Royal Panda 對 1001 名遊戲玩家進行了 4 部分的智商測試。研究集中在 4 個關鍵，分別是：語言智力、數學能力、邏輯推理和視覺推理。研究結果顯示，PC 玩家最聰明，集體智商為 112.3。緊隨其後的是 PS 玩家，為110.7，Xbox 玩家為 103.8，Switch 玩家為 101.3，手遊玩家則墊底，僅得 99.4。<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2818291/%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8C%87%E7%8E%A9%20PC%20%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%20IQ%20%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%20%20%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%A9%20......\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2818291%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%258E%25A9%2520PC%2520%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%2520IQ%2520%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%2520%2520%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%258E%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%258E%25A9%2520......&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=3bb90746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2818291/%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8C%87%E7%8E%A9%20PC%20%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%20IQ%20%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%20%20%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%A9%20......</a>"},{"pid":"b27a2a274a0e230927d5b89984006e8824d89d2e","tid":2318141,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"講啲唔講啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9456d2e0c7b98b4da50feeb6dfc9bacfc8dacf5","tid":2318141,"uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"自動行 自動打怪都玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" cl